extendedInfo.description: Maher Zain is a Muslim Swedish R&B singer, songwriter and music producer of Lebanese origin. He is very famous for his religious Islamic songs.This App is all about Maher Zain. You can get his song's lyrics, his videos, and his biography.Get the lyrics of his songs:- Allahi Allah Kiya Karo- Always Be There- Awaken- Barakallah- For The Rest of My Life- Freedom- Hold My Hand- I Believe (Feat. Irfan Makki)- Insha Allah- Love Will Prevail- Open Your Eyes- Palestine Will Be Free- Ramadan (English Version)- Ramadan (Malay-Bahasa Version)- Ramadan (Turkish Version)- Sepanjang Hidup- Thank You Allah- The Chosen One- Ya Nabi Salam AlaykaDisclaimer: This app contains a video section, in organized way to browse and view YouTube Videos. If you found any of your video in the app, and you'd like them removed, please let us know and we will immediately remove it from the app itself.This is an unofficial free fans app. Any content not owned by the developer belongs to their respective owners. If you would like to request removal of any image for copyright reasons, feel free to contact us.
